
.TH beings2 1 "June 17, 2026"
.SH NAME
beings2 \- Text-mode battle simulator.
.PP
.SH SYNOPSIS
beings2
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
Successor to beings. Instead of a pure simple AI simulator as the predecessor, this program is also a two-team battle simulator. Each being has individual decision making depending on surrounding and other beings. In attack mode, every being will try to attack whenever a being in the opposite team is sighted.
.PP
